title: NFL ATL: Super Bowl XLVIII recap
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Super Bowl XLVIII recap
description:
On the Super Bowl XLVIII edition of the ATL Podcast, the crew breaks down how the Seattle Seahawks dominated the Denver Broncos from start to finish, and whether a dynasty could be brewing in the Pacific Northwest. Did the blowout loss tarnish Peyton Manning's legacy? The gang hits on all that -- and more.
